      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the most exacting standards. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no mechanical or cosmetic imperfections. Its provenance and care are evident in every detail, offering an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade motorcar.",
