    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it looks and drives like a dream. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
