    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is an exemplary specimen of Porsche\u2019s water-cooled engineering. It features the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and lift. Power is delivered through a G96 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring mechanical grip and surgical shift precision. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a corner-balanced suspension. Critically, this vehicle has a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a clean bore scope report, confirming its mechanical longevity. With flawless paint depth and an interior free of bolster wear or dash shrinkage, this is a collector-grade driver\u2019s car.",
